{
  "stem": "27335.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, it was Churchill's plot who actually arranged the Yugoslav uprising.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was the one who proclaimed Tito marshal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was Churchill.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And two days later of uprising, Churchill's son, Randolph Churchill, parachuted into Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then the rest of it you probably know, somehow, at least some.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From there, well then-- then we waited very restlessly, because of the situation in-- in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But to just [INAUDIBLE] coming back to her entering, and to finish with her, then she-- she crossed the [INAUDIBLE] with this company.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in about three [INAUDIBLE] they were captured.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then-- then later it was noticeable in the prison already that-- that mission was, I mean, the crossing, the crossing place was already exposed by the-- by the Hungarian counterintelligence military [INAUDIBLE], or by the gendarme, or by-- by-- by-- by somebody.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I will know this, because one of the Canadian Hungarian which was my group, he was on the same prisoner's train from Pec, from southern Hungary, from the [INAUDIBLE] Yugoslav border, where they were shipped up to-- up to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Hannah-- Hannah tried to escape.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then the books that have been written about her, they even called her a coward and so on, that she wanted to commit suicide.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's why she jumped the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But like hell.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She jumped the train to try to escape.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She had courage.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She had guts.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they captured her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was one, who the Hungarian comrade, who was on the same train with her, on the prison train.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they captured her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, yes, yes, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well he will say he-- he was-- he was also captured and same-- same.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
